S. Leach (SISSA)

See test_get_planet_temperature.pro for a test driver.

Returned peak temperature assumes solid angle for a
symmetric gaussian beam when aligned with planet.

Brightness temperature of Jupiter and Saturn based on Moreno'98
model.

Possible improvements:
- Solid angle for elliptical planets.
- Implement Lagrange point 2 (1.01 AU from Sun).
